fix_approach:
Add a useEffect in main.tsx that monitors the unread count for the currently selected contact. When the count increases from 0 to N (indicating new messages arrived), automatically call markMessagesRead. This ensures messages are marked as read both on manual selection (existing behavior) and when they arrive in an already-open conversation (new behavior).

Pseudocode:
```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  if (
    selectedIdentityId &&
    selectedContactId &&
    nostling.unreadCounts[selectedIdentityId]?.[selectedContactId] > 0
  ) {
    void nostling.markMessagesRead(selectedIdentityId, selectedContactId);
  }
}, [selectedIdentityId, selectedContactId, nostling.unreadCounts, nostling.markMessagesRead]);
```
